properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued January 13 at 8:20AM CST until January 14 at 9:00AM CST by NWS New Orleans LA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Visibility one quarter mile or less in dense fog.

* WHERE...Lower Plaquemines County.

* WHEN...Dense Fog Advisory, until 3 PM CST this afternoon then
again from 6 PM this evening to 9 AM CST Tuesday and may need to
be extended after that.

* IMPACTS...Hazardous driving conditions due to low visibility.
properties.instruction:
If driving, slow down, use your headlights, and leave plenty of
distance ahead of you.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 3 PM CST THIS AFTERNOON... ...DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 6 PM THIS EVENING TO 9 AM CST TUESDAY
